After installing flask via pip install, you should have most, if not all, of the modules in the requirements.txt.

To run the application paste this command into your command prompt/terminal:
Mac/Unix:
FLASK_APP=sudoku.py flask run

OR

export FLASK_APP=sudoku.py
flask run

Windows:
$env:FLASK_APP=sudoku.py
flask run

OR

$env:FLASK_APP=sudoku.py
python -m flask run

The website will not be generated automatically. Go into your browser of choice and paste the link given by the program.
Example: http://127.0.0.1:5000